                            <p rend="flushleft">Subject: <gloss target="#t_UN1">UN</gloss>
                                Contributions—1952 Budget</p>
                            <p>In continuing the next steps in Delegation action concerning the
                                problem of contributions to the regular <gloss target="#t_UN1">UN</gloss> budget, the Representatives and staff will probably
